<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>You’ll find many savings across our <strong>2017/18</strong> ski program, with discounts of up to £400 per couple (at the <a data-udi="umb://document/c1c83e1d39df4402b53d288cd57e1a81" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c1c83e1d39df4402b53d288cd57e1a81}" title="Hotel Alpenrose">Hotel Alpenrose, Alpe d'Huez</a>) when you book early!</p>
<p>Check the Inghams Plus deals on the <strong>'Special Offers' tab</strong> on individual hotel descriptions to find the savings and other offers available for <strong>Ski 2017/18</strong>.</p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" title="Ski Resorts">Search Ski Holidays &gt;</a></h2>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Applies to bookings made for the 2017/18 ski season.</li>
<li>All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publishing, are subject to change &amp; availability and can be withdrawn at any time.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
